posts.name: Mason Braden
posts.cooked: Its possible to work well without ground intake, but its way more reliable than station pickup.
Worth it, yes very much. Is my team going to do it, no probably not.

posts.name: Will C
posts.cooked: Its worth it, but is definitely a second priority. Develop a human player intake and then a ground intake is my advice.

And for the record, I only eat donuts off the floor at week 4 regionals.
